Transformation.Name: Transform
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10075" AS ( SELECT /*+ inline */ "CASE_ID", "CO2_EMMISIONS_KT", "COUNTRY_CODE", "COUNTRY_NAME", "DISASTER_TYPE", "FOREST_AREA_PERC_LAND_AREA", "FOSSIL_FUEL_PERC_ENERGY_CONS", "GDP_US_DOLLARS", "INT_USERS_PER_HUNDRED_PPL", "MBL_SUBSCR_PER_HUNDRED_PPL", "METHAN_EMISSIONS_KT", "NITR_OX_EMISSIONS_KT", "OCCURRENCE", "PERCENT_AGRICULTURAL_LAND", "PERC_TOTAL_PUB_HEALTH_EXP", "PERC_URB_POPULATION", "POPULATION", "POWER_CONS_KWH_PER_CAPITA", "TOTAL_AFFECTED", "YEAR", case when "AFFECTED" < 211 then 1 when "AFFECTED" >= 211 and "AFFECTED"< 6000 then 2 when "AFFECTED" >= 6000 and "AFFECTED"< 77000 then 3 when "AFFECTED" >= 77000 then 4 when "AFFECTED" IS NULL then 5 end "AFFECTED_BIN", case when "DEATHS" < 4 then 1 when "DEATHS" >= 4 and "DEATHS"< 20 then 2 when "DEATHS" >= 20 and "DEATHS"< 97 then 3 when "DEATHS" >= 97 then 4 when "DEATHS" IS NULL then 5 end "DEATHS_BIN", case when "HOMELESS" <= 7000000 then 1 when "HOMELESS" IS NULL then 2 end "HOMELESS_BIN" , case when "INJURED" <= 13 then 1 when "INJURED" = 600000 then 2 when "INJURED" IS NULL then 3 end "INJURED_BIN" , case when "TOTAL_DAMAGE" <= 30000 then 1 when "TOTAL_DAMAGE" = 210000000 then 2 when "TOTAL_DAMAGE" IS NULL then 3 end "TOTAL_DAMAGE_BIN" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )
